{
  "texts": [
    "Experimental designThis experiment uses natural language processing (NLP) technology to improve drug recommendation systems tailored to individual patient conditions.",
    "The experimental methods followed a structured methodology that included data exploration, data preprocessing, model development, conclusion and limitation assessment.",
    "In the data exploration phase, visualization and statistical techniques are used to gain insight into the characteristics of the data set.",
    "This process helps to pre-process the data and engineer the relevant features for the model.",
    "To address the limitations inherent in natural language processing, we introduce the LightGBM machine learning model."
  ]
}